        "translation": "He then heard about the ten recollections teaching.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c09_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "急忙之中。",
        "translation": "In his haste, he took incense, placed it in his palms, and burned it.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c10_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "取香安放手掌焚燒。",
        "translation": "He puts incense in his palms and burns it.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c10_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "力求超度。",
        "translation": "He strives to transcend [his suffering].",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c10_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尚可見佛接引。",
        "translation": "He can still see the Buddha and be guided.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c11_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "得了下品下生。",
        "translation": "They'll be reborn in a lower class or lower birth.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c11_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何況生平行為。",
        "translation": "It's even more so when their conduct in life is ordinary.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c11_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尚不至於十惡五逆。",
        "translation": "It doesn't even reach the level of the ten evils and five heinous crimes.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c12_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而又起信得早。",
        "translation": "They've also arisen early in life to believe.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c12_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "豈有不遂往生之理。",
        "translation": "How could it be possible that he won't be reborn?",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c12_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故念佛不可希求來世福報。",
        "translation": "Therefore, mindfulness of the Buddha shouldn't aspire to the merit of the future.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c13_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "到得福報盡時。",
        "translation": "When the rewards of merit are exhausted, they'll still be subject to suffering.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c13_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依然要受苦楚。",
        "translation": "I'll still have to suffer.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c14_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "那裏比得跳出輪迴。",
        "translation": "That's better than jumping out of the cycle of rebirth.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c14_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能彀永享極樂的好。",
        "translation": "It's better to be able to enjoy eternal bliss.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c14_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "惟求父母往生。",
        "translation": "You should only seek the rebirth of your parents.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c15_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及在世保病。",
        "translation": "He'll preserve his illness in the world and look after those who have passed away.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c15_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "去世追薦的。",
        "translation": "Those who go to the afterlife will be honored.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c15_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "皆是孝思。",
        "translation": "These are all filial thoughts.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c16_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "可以求得。",
        "translation": "They can be sought.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c16_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但父母在世的。",
        "translation": "But for those whose parents are still alive.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c16_23",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不若勸其自念的好。",
        "translation": "It's better to encourage them to think of themselves.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c16_24",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "昔長蘆頤禪師勸孝文云。",
        "translation": "In the past, Seon Master Jōrohei advised Hōshō Man.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c17_25",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能勸父母修淨土。",
        "translation": "\"Someone who encourages their parents to cultivate the Pure Land.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c17_26",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是為大孝。",
        "translation": "This is great filial piety.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c18_27",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今世人得見此書。",
        "translation": "Now, people in the world can see this book.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c18_28",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "就是有緣。",
        "translation": "That's when they have the right conditions.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c18_29",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "宜發堅信心。",
        "translation": "They should have a strong faith.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c19_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "勸父母戚友。",
        "translation": "They should encourage their parents, relatives, and friends.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c19_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一同念佛。",
        "translation": "They should chant the Buddha's name together.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c19_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "莫教當面錯過。",
        "translation": "Don't let them miss it face to face.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c19_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "倘或轉勸未能兄信。",
        "translation": "Perhaps he'll turn around and fail to encourage his brother's faith.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c20_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "却已曉得天地間。",
        "translation": "Yet, you've already realized that there's something in heaven and earth.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c20_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "原有這超出輪迴。",
        "translation": "There really is this way of transcending transmigration.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c20_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "投生極樂的法門。",
        "translation": "It's the dharma-gate of rebirth in paradise.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c21_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "耳根聽熟。",
        "translation": "He's heard it well in his ears.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c21_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "日久自然會信。",
        "translation": "As time goes by, he'll naturally believe it.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c21_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至於戒殺。",
        "translation": "As for the precept against killing, he should only eat the three pure forms of meat.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c22_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但食三淨肉。",
        "translation": "He simply eats the three pure forms of meat.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c22_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不傷生命。",
        "translation": "It doesn't harm life.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c22_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "便是佛家以眼不見其殺。",
        "translation": "That's the Buddhist way of saying that the eye doesn't see it and the ear doesn't hear it.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c22_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "耳不聞其殺。",
        "translation": "Their ears don't hear that it's killing.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c23_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心不疑其因我而殺。",
        "translation": "Their minds don't doubt that it's killed because of themselves.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c23_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "名為三淨肉。",
        "translation": "This is called the three pure forms of meat.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c24_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "便可食得。",
        "translation": "You can then eat them.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c24_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如能長年食素更佳。",
        "translation": "It's even better if you can stay a vegetarian for a long time.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c24_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "凡修淨業。",
        "translation": "\"Everyone cultivates pure activities.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0364c24_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "除念佛外。",
        "translation": "Apart from mindfulness of the Buddha, the only thing they should do is recite the true words of the Pure Land.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0365a01_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "惟誦淨土真言。",
        "translation": "He should only recite the true words of the Pure Land.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0365a01_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "超度一切眾生。",
        "translation": "It's to transcend all sentient beings.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0365a01_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "往生西方則可。",
        "translation": "Rebirth in the West is then possible.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0365a01_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "餘與淨土無涉。",
        "translation": "The rest has nothing to do with the Pure Land.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0365a02_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "昔蓮池大師臨終時。",
        "translation": "Once upon a time, when the great Lianchi master was about to die.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0365a02_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "果然見佛來迎。",
        "translation": "He really did see the Buddha coming to greet him.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0365a03_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "因叮嚀大眾云。",
        "translation": "He exhorted the crowd, saying.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0365a03_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "老實念佛。",
        "translation": "\"Recite the Buddha's name honestly.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0365a03_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "莫換題目。",
        "translation": "Don't change the title.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0365a03_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "可見三藏十二部經。",
        "translation": "You can see the 12 scriptures of the Tripiṭaka.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0365a04_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "同那八萬四千法門。",
        "translation": "It's the same as those 84,000 dharma teachings.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0365a04_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "總不若念佛為第一也。",
        "translation": "It's always unlike recitation of the Buddha, which is the best.",
        "source": "X01n0013_001:0365a04_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    }
]